name: Stylish Stud #9088
description: A 15,008-piece combined collection of Studs and Mares. They came together to produce the very first racehorses in Photo Finish™ LIVE - laying down the bloodlines that run through every horse in the game. PFP owners are VIP’s in the ecosystem, receiving $CROWN based on overall rarity, and gaining entry into the exclusive Photo Finish™ Jockey Club.
